{"tid":1165433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子訛稱與女友慶生　長洲租度假屋燒炭昏迷","createTime":"2019-05-21T19:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T01:29:24.000Z","uid":234553,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9bbcee4cf0c16e0bd766d09e8bdd9dfc4f558478","tid":1165433,"uid":234553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522010859335-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190522025936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522010859335-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190522025936&h=76ffd116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灰爆男「度計」長洲租度假屋燒炭自殺。昨日(21日)傍晚6時許，一名28歲姓陳男子到長洲東堤小築租度假屋，他向訛稱替女友慶祝生日，屋主不虞有詐租住給他，惟2小時後，屋主仍未見其「女友」出現察覺可疑，致電租屋男子查詢，但無人接聽。屋主隨即上門，並用後備鎖匙開門，赫見該名男子於浴室內燒炭，昏迷不醒，大驚報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員將昏迷事主送往長洲醫院，再由直升機轉送出東區醫院，現場未有檢獲遺書，警方正調查事主輕生原因。"},{"pid":"e4171b563a700d26e6ec98cca02e984a2489352c","tid":1165433,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T21:58:55.000Z","msg":"自殺失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />間屋差啲變凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb4ad1244ce5b52d790d7048e1d8eeeab93a661","tid":1165433,"uid":58590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:00:59.000Z","msg":"長洲應該真係間間都有事⋯⋯唔撚敢再去"},{"pid":"f0f857d16c5a941d65718f8f556add5bf289ad4f","tid":1165433,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:01:01.000Z","msg":"冇講大話，下世先有女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2d53e484972e930ae97310c4b7769012ba4ac4","tid":1165433,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T22:11:06.000Z","msg":"屋主好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0efbba659d965c32b6c15